name: Boa Hancock (ボア･ハンコック) One Piece Character LoRA
description:
Trained on AnyLora

Please note that with some enhancers(Detail Tweaker, e.t.c.) it is very easy to get better results than showcased, since i didn't use any to generate showcase images for this LoRA

To get the best results, please read the description below:

  • Recommended weight for V1: 0.6-0.8

  • Recommended weight for V2: 0.65-0.85

  • Activation word for V1: BoaHancock

  • Activation word for V1: BoaHancockV2

  • Use of "Detail Tweaker LoRA" is also recommended for good results

  • Upscale to 1.5

  • Using anime SD models is recommended, semi-realistic checkpoints also work quite well

I would appreciate any reviews, positive or negative!

I would very much appreciate you sharing your results ^_^

If you have any suggestions on what LoRA i should do next, please share them in the comments

Enjoy :)
